            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Our Waste Services deliver value by helping customers manage their lower activity waste efficiently to reduce disposal volumes and preserve capacity at the Low-Level Waste Repository. Customers can access a wide range of treatment and disposal services to ensure waste is managed in accordance with the waste hierarchy.</P>
               <P>The current WTS frameworks expire on 30 June 2018. There is a requirement to ensure the service is available post-June 2018 to ensure LLWR can continue to deliver the National LLW Programme three strategic themes whilst capitalizing on opportunities to enhance LLWR’s service offerings to customers, as well as achieving efficiencies by combining multiple Lots into one single tender capability based Lot.</P>
               <P>LLWR intends to procure a multi-supplier Framework Agreement for the provision of a range of WTS. The Framework Agreement will be available to any organization that holds a Waste Services Contract with LLWR.</P>
